  "remarks": "The ownership of the entity was transferred contrary to Ukrainian law. On 9 April 2014, the “Presidium of the Parliament of Crimea” adopted decision No 1991-6/14 “On the amendments to the Resolution of the State Council of the ‘Republic of Crimea’” of 26 March 2014 No 1836-6/14 “On nationalisation of the property of enterprises, institutions and organisations of agro-industrial complex, located in the territory of the ‘Republic of Crimea’” declaring the appropriation of assets belonging to the state enterprise “Zavod shampanskykh vin Novy Svet” on behalf of the “Republic of Crimea”.",
